        "banner_text": "<p class=\"section-banner__text\">Buy a new pair of gloves and see a thin layer of plastic on the palm?</p>\n<p class=\"section-banner__text\">That’s not a defect — it’s there for protection.</p>\n<p class=\"section-banner__text\">Most of our adult gloves come with a thin plastic film across the latex. It keeps the grip fresh during shipping and storage. But before you wear them, you need to peel it off. Properly.</p>"
