      "settings": {
        "title": "Final Tip",
        "description": "<p class=\"section-help-text__text\">Don’t peel the film weeks in advance.</p>\n<p class=\"section-help-text__text\">Don’t store gloves with half-peeled latex.</p>\n<p class=\"section-help-text__text\">And definitely don’t forget to remove it before a match — or you’ll find out the hard way why the grip feels wrong.</p>"
